{"tid":620004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬時亨：港鐵一直補貼乘客　有需要加價改善服務","createTime":"2018-04-07T07:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T11:37:34.000Z","uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"26724f1632eda458b814298b3896533ba5e6ae45","tid":620004,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】高鐵列車試運期間在石崗列車停放處偏離路軌，港鐵主席馬時亨表示，事件不會影響通車時間。他認為，能在試運期間發現問題是好事，強調會以安全為首要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n一列高鐵列車星期二晚在石崗列事停放處部分車輪偏離路軌，有路軌的工字鐵變形。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨表示，目前已初步掌握成因，如果批評港鐵隱瞞是不智和不合邏輯。他認為，能在試運期間發現問題是好事，暫時不會影響在九月底通車的目標。<br />\n<br />\n根據票價調整機制，港鐵今年會加價3.14%。馬時亨表示，港鐵股東在車務收益上的回報只有百分之1，形容為「幾乎打和」，一直要靠物業收益來補貼乘客。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，港鐵多年來加價都低於通脹，令市民乘坐港鐵的車費佔生活開支越來越低。而去年凍結票價，今年有需要加價才能夠維持和改善服務質素。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨指，如果政府回購港鐵，日後仍要動用公帑補貼，亦會影響其他公共交通，政府需要詳細考慮甚麼做法才是對市民最好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=301544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D301544&d=oOx0PQo6li7FOOuXmjG%2ByF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=fb845c29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D301544&h=77d9fddb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=301544</a>"},{"pid":"1f6b34411f421600ce25f69ec730f3757dd589fa","tid":620004,"uid":1767,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n價就加左咁多年 服務幾時有好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd4d65116c1b8d0d0c4f105dadb4038af23736b","tid":620004,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:13:07.000Z","msg":"調轉咗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係要加價之後補貼少少畀乘客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388cd58beaaa14347abc4b67ca83853ab8fe62cb","tid":620004,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:14:06.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n唔係有咁多人流<br />\n你收撚到咁多租咩<br />\n係乘客帶物業收益咋屎忽鬼"},{"pid":"9c3324d1d5fb2ee0e922759dbf21ec4dfbaaae56","tid":620004,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ff63b916e5f0dd3f1783ffaa142b2de6a3cbc6","tid":620004,"uid":19609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"好似係因為你服務有問題，有罰款先要補貼返。<br />\n<br />\n家下補貼完又加返價？"},{"pid":"fe110176ee6f80d6ee4b68f82ebb61b739acf589","tid":620004,"uid":78016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"狗鐵只求打個和 大家坐得開開心心就可以<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c12484195e11292243cc38521b78582a4210efd","tid":620004,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:18:35.000Z","msg":"當年起幕門都要我地俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606d56331bb6864c12870abaf73bc354e9e6cdd5","tid":620004,"uid":102096,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e29912e15ed7fbf47c69aa16f224812102666cfe","tid":620004,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"唔好起樓囉，1%車務回報喎"},{"pid":"03f78ef63f0df34db0bb1154c5041b64535ea052","tid":620004,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"地鐵只求打過和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大家開開心心搭返轉<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9d74deec682b0b7b096a1c6